(Executive summary) Tj
T*
(- Block time: 120 seconds \(262,800 blocks/year\).) Tj
T*
(- Era size: 1,314,000 blocks \(5 years\).) Tj
T*
(- First 5 eras follow 10 -> 5 -> 2.5 -> 1.25 -> 0.625 ATHO/block.) Tj
T*
(- Then reward is fixed at 0.3125 ATHO/block until exact supply reaches 30,000,000 ATHO.) Tj
T*
(- Tail starts at height 21,102,000 \(year ~80.3\) with 0.25 ATHO/block forever.) Tj
T*
(- Tail annual issuance is fixed at 65,700 ATHO/year.) Tj
T*
(- Fee floor is 200 atoms/vB \(2.0e-7 ATHO/vB\).) Tj
T*
(- Post-tail split target is 100% burn / 0% miner fee share, clipped by floor headroom.) Tj
T*
(- Supply floor is 21,000,000 ATHO.) Tj
T*
(- Protocol deflation threshold is exactly 50% sustained block-byte utilization.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
