T*
() Tj
T*
(Fee and burn math) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Per block at full utilization) Tj
T*
(- Max fee pool per full block: 2,500,000 * 200 atoms = 500,000,000 atoms = 0.5 ATHO) Tj
T*
(- Tail issuance per block: 0.25 ATHO) Tj
T*
(- Net per-block change formula: Delta_block = 0.25 - \(0.5 * utilization\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Per year at full utilization) Tj
T*
(- Tail issuance: 0.25 * 262,800 = 65,700 ATHO/year) Tj
T*
(- Max annual fee pool: 2,500,000 * 262,800 * 2.0e-7 = 131,400 ATHO/year) Tj
T*
(- Annual net formula: Delta_year = 65,700 - \(131,400 * utilization\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
